<chapter xml:id="hypothesis-testing">
  <title>Hypothesis testing</title>
  
  <introduction>
    <p>
      This chapter introduces the framework of hypothesis testing for making decisions based on data.
    </p>
  </introduction>

  <section xml:id="null-hypothesis">
    <title>The null hypothesis</title>
    <p>
      Hypothesis testing begins with formulating null and alternative hypotheses.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section xml:id="p-values">
    <title>P-values and statistical significance</title>
    <p>
      P-values quantify the evidence against the null hypothesis.
    </p>
  </section>
